<H3> <TI>   UNESCO To Cooperate in Cultural Affairs </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1502221494 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1820 GMT 15 Feb 
94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW1502221494 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, February 15 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- 
Mongolia and UNESCO have decided to cooperate in the sphere of 
culture, elaborate a number of programmes in this direction. 
First of all, within the framework of cooperation with this big 
international organization a work will be carried out on 
protection, popularization in abroad of historical and cultural 
monuments of Mongolia. It is planned to shoot documentaries and 
TV films, organize tourist trips. Besides that, UNESCO will 
render assistance to Mongolia in strengthening material 
facilities of the Mongolian National University of Culture and 
Art, in elaboration of the national policy in the sphere of 
culture. 

</TEXT>

