the middle of January. Others accompanying Marut at the 
luncheon included Chawarin Latthasaksiri -- Cai Junrong -- Chat 
Thai Party MP for Rat Buri Province who has visited Taiwan 
several times; Charoen Khanthawong, Democrat Party MP for 
Bangkok; Parliament Secretary Phasit Phiphatthanakun; and Zheng 
Yousu [Thai name: Suthikiat Chirathiwat] of the Central Plaza 
Hotel. 

