of our party and wisely guiding the work for its realization, 
such as "the dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il proclaiming the 
modelling of the whole society on the chuche idea as the supreme 
programme of our party" and "the dear leader Comrade Kim 
Chong-il, an illustrious thinker and theoretician". 
