Asia and the world. The two sides have reiterated the intention 
of their respective governments to strengthen relations and 
cooperation in various fields, in particular in the economic, 
trade, scientific, and technical fields, between the two 
countries for the common benefits of the Lao and Indonesian 
peoples. 
  H.E. Ali Alatas, foreign affairs minister of the Republic of 
